data: The Aurora Casino is the largest gambling establishment in the network, known for drawing in hopeful gamblers from all over the galaxy. In this bustling venue, tourists mix with thugs and gangsters, as the station also serves as an unofficial gathering place for the Vigor Syndicate and other shady organisations.
